{"tid":2463532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Zerohedge: 印度發現首例 \"雙突變 \"COVID菌株，新病例激增","createTime":"2021-03-26T18:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T19:37:54.000Z","uid":294518,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bf637f2492a9e521130e56e07b60f10ad546a2e3","tid":2463532,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.zerohedge.com/covid-19/india-discovers-first-double-mutant-covid-strain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zerohedge.com%2Fcovid-19%2Findia-discovers-first-double-mutant-covid-strain&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=6221d7f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zerohedge.com/covid-19/india-discovers-first-double-mutant-covid-strain</a><br />\n<br />\nZerohedge: 印度發現首例 &quot;雙突變 &quot;COVID菌株，新病例激增。<br />\n<br />\n繼巴西、美國等地首次發現的變異COVID病毒株在拉丁美洲、美國和歐洲等地傳播的一系列報告發出警告後，印度的科學家們一鼓作氣，確定了他們所描述的這種無處不在的病毒的 &quot;雙變異 &quot;株。<br />\n<br />\n該 &quot;雙突變體 &quot;與其他770個菌株一起，從印度18個邦收集的樣本中被確認。在收集到的10,787個樣本中，736個樣本對英國變種呈陽性，34個樣本對南非變種呈陽性，1個樣本對巴西變種呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n印度曾設法將病例數字降至接近清零，在該報告發佈之際，印度的武肺病例再次攀升。該國報告的病例總數為11.7MM，死亡人數為16.04萬。"},{"pid":"9d8ed394d7681503460bcd1bd460adc1bf91d7dd","tid":2463532,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T18:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfHeapfgBfWBEu5eJnoKMRSwViM3AmsXFKD7Mr4fYjb55?filename=zFiDo6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFiDo6K.png&h=d7499f84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b176dbd39afd189777da185b7bc44f701e93e9a3","tid":2463532,"uid":13804,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T18:52:56.000Z","msg":"真係唔撚識停，支那仆街<br />\n隨時要玩10年"},{"pid":"4754cc07f2b48d2bc2815af85bdf30540d279d67","tid":2463532,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T18:56:58.000Z","msg":"十年熊市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hk